-- Bridgepoint May Buy CMA CGM’s Cruise Unit, Sunday Times Says
-- B y   E m m a   C h a r l t o n
-- 2012-07-15T10:00:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-15/bridgepoint-may-buy-cma-cgm-s-cruise-unit-sunday-times-says.html
Bridgepoint Capital Ltd. may buy CMA
CGM SA’s cruise unit, Compagnie du Ponant, the Sunday Times
reported without saying where it got the information.  The deal may be agreed next month, the  newspaper  said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
